The '''2014 [[Philippine National Games]]''' was held in [[Metro Manila]], [[Philippines]] from May 16–25, 2014.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Terrado|first1=Reuben|title=Manila to host 2014 Philippine National Games in May|url=http://www.spin.ph/sports/multi-sport-events/news/manila-to-host-2014-philippine-national-games-in-may|accessdate=29 November 2015|publisher=Sports Interactive Network Philippines|date=11 May 2014}}</ref> The opening ceremony was held at the [[Ninoy Aquino Stadium]] in [[Manila]] on May 15, 2014.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Calapre|first1=Frank|title=Philippine National Games unfolds today|url=http://www.manilatimes.net/philippine-national-games-unfolds-today/96813/|accessdate=29 November 2015|publisher=The Manila Times|date=15 May 2014}}</ref>
