'''Club Vaca Díez''' is a [[Bolivia]]n football club based in [[Cobija]], [[Pando Department|Pando]]. The club was founded March 19, 1952 and competes in the [[Liga Nacional B]] from the team's home base, [[Estadio Roberto Jordán]].

