[[File:Mar Bella Centre Esportiu (Barcelona).JPG|thumb|Pavelló de la Mar Bella]] The '''Pavelló de la Mar Bella''' is an [[indoor arena]] located in [[Barcelona]], [[Catalonia]]. Seating 4000, it hosted the [[Badminton at the 1992 Summer Olympics|badminton]] events for [[1992 Summer Olympics]].
This venue was completed in time for the 1992 Games.
==References== *[http://www.la84foundation.org/6oic/OfficialReports/1992/1992s2.pdf 1992 Summer Olympics official report.] Volume 2. pp.&nbsp;259–62.
